attributes.Long form description: The student is assembling a nightstand. They begin by attaching the legs to the middle shelf, then screw the top shelf onto the legs. They finish by screwing the top trays onto the top shelf.

attributes.Transcription: Hello and welcome to our study.
In front of you, you will see the parts needed to assemble, a nightstand from Ikea.
Your task for now will be to please assemble it.

attributes.Action sentence: The student assembles the first leg to the middle shelf of the nightstand.

attributes.Transcription: Please take one of the shelves and place it vertically on the table on its long side.
Please screw in one of the feet on top left side of the shelf.
Begin in the middle hole of the foot.

attributes.Incorrect Action Explanation: The student drops the allen wrench.
